# BMI Calculator

This is a simple BMI (Body Mass Index) Calculator built using React and styled with Tailwind CSS. The application allows users to calculate their BMI based on their weight and height, and provides a classification of their BMI result.

Features

- Calculate BMI based on weight and height inputs.
- Provides BMI classification (Underweight, Normal weight, Overweight).
- Responsive design with Tailwind CSS.
- Easy-to-use interface.

Installation

To get a local copy up and running, follow these simple steps:

1. Clone the repository:

   bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/bmi-calculator.git

2. Navigate to the project directory:

    cd BMI-Calculator

3. Install the dependencies:

     npm install

4. Usage
    Once the dependencies are installed, you can start the development server:
      npm start

This will start the application and open it in your default web browser at http://localhost:3000

Calculating BMI
1.Enter your weight in Ibs.
2.Enter your height in meters (m).
3.Click on the "Submit" button.
4.Your BMI and its classification will be displayed.
